data.description: Beautiful 2016 PALM HARBOR (Real Property) on 3+ acres. The large modern farmhouse kitchen has island with breakfast bar, farmhouse sink, & double pane windows that provide great natural light in kitchen & dining room. Lg living room has built in bookshelves & space for TV. Dining room has window seat & a barn door pantry. Split bedrooms with master bedroom & master bath with double sinks, garden tub, & separate shower with seat. All bedrooms have walk-in closets. Front & back porches & patio. You will enjoy the country living. With your RV you could use the fenced off area for family to visit or income possibilities. Aerobic septic system and FHA required tiedowns installed in 2020.
